03:12.651 --> 03:14.235
I want to talk to you

03:12.651 --> 03:14.235
for a minute.

03:14.277 --> 03:15.654
Now, when I get home,

03:15.696 --> 03:18.239
I get to plug this cord

03:15.696 --> 03:18.239
back into the TV.

03:18.281 --> 03:21.242
So you boys have to behave.

03:21.284 --> 03:25.039
