04:13.962 --> 04:15.296
Huh?

04:13.962 --> 04:15.296
No TV.

04:15.338 --> 04:18.299
No friends... till tomorrow.

04:18.341 --> 04:20.301
But, Mom...

04:18.341 --> 04:20.301
This is the last Sunday

04:20.343 --> 04:21.678
of your punishment.

04:21.720 --> 04:23.513
But...

04:21.720 --> 04:23.513
