07:44.423 --> 07:46.507
The manager there has

07:44.423 --> 07:46.507
a pretty enlightened outlook

07:46.549 --> 07:48.135
about a kid's right to choose

07:46.549 --> 07:48.135
his own school hours.

07:48.176 --> 07:49.677
We don't have

07:48.176 --> 07:49.677
any money, though.

07:49.719 --> 07:51.305
All right, you guys

07:49.719 --> 07:51.305
are doing me a favor,

07:51.346 --> 07:53.307
so I'm gonna let you in

07:51.346 --> 07:53.307
on a little secret.

07:53.348 --> 07:54.515
Mom keeps some money

07:54.557 --> 07:56.684
in the top left drawer

07:54.557 --> 07:56.684
of her dresser,

07:56.726 --> 07:58.186
but she won't notice

07:58.228 --> 08:00.521
