09:40.663 --> 09:41.622
No!

09:41.664 --> 09:44.209
He wouldn't do that.

09:41.664 --> 09:44.209
You did it!

09:44.251 --> 09:45.668
Shut up!

09:44.251 --> 09:45.668
He sold us out!

09:45.710 --> 09:47.628
Francis is dead

09:45.710 --> 09:47.628
to us now!

09:47.670 --> 09:49.672
Wait a minute--

09:49.714 --> 09:51.674
that makes me

09:49.714 --> 09:51.674
the oldest brother.

09:51.716 --> 09:53.009
Guys, seriously--

09:53.051 --> 09:55.636
if you have any problems,

09:53.051 --> 09:55.636
you can come to me.

09:55.678 --> 09:56.888
Dewey, get me some ice tea.

09:56.930 --> 09:58.098
No!

09:59.474 --> 10:01.476
We should just give this to Mom

09:59.474 --> 10:01.476
